Package com.deloitte.tsc.transformers

This package contains classes that are used for transformation purposes.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractConcatenationTransformer
    Abstract class used by all of the concatenation transformers, for the purpose of centralizing common code.
    StringBufferTransformer
    This class is used for performing a transformation in which a string is concatenated to over and over again (with the number of iterations specified by the numIterations flow variable), via the StringBuffer class.
    StringBuilderTransformer
    This class is used for performing a transformation in which a string is concatenated to over and over again (with the number of iterations specified by the numIterations flow variable), via the StringBuilder class.
    StringConcatenationTransformer
    This class is used for performing a transformation in which a string is concatenated to over and over again (with the number of iterations specified by the numIterations flow variable), via simple string concatenation.
    TestDriverResultTransformer
    This class is used to generate the output response to the Test Driver API.

Package com.deloitte.tsc.transformers Description

This package contains classes that are used for transformation purposes. In some cases, the results of the transformations are not actually used for anything – they are simply performed, so that the time it takes for the transformation can be calculated.
Author:
David Hunter, Deloitte
